description:
That's right! "Touhou LostWord" songs have found their way to Spell Bubble!
Featuring 6 songs from the popular MV Project!
Enjoy a luxurious collection of songs in which the finest vocalists collab with popular music circles!

This pack contains the following:

■6 Songs
・The Heat of My Fingertips / Touhou LostWord feat. feat. Shimamiya Eiko × Yuuhei Satellite
・Sporadically Margaret / Touhou LostWord feat. konoco × ShinRa-Bansho
・Silver Gale / Touhou LostWord feat. Nanase Aikawa × BUTAOTOME
・NAЯAKA / Touhou LostWord feat. kaguranana × SOUND HOLIC
・I'm Alright! / Touhou LostWord feat. KIHOW from MYTH & ROID × A-One
・PHANTOM PAIN / Touhou LostWord feat. KOTOKO × ZYTOKINE

■6 Challenge Stages
・Lv.5 Where Did I Leave It? (I'm Alright!)
・Lv.6 Game of Bubbles (Silver Gale)
・Lv.7 Want Me to Cool It Down? (The Heat of My Fingertips)
・Lv.8 Cry for the moon (PHANTOM PAIN)
・Lv.9 Spell Bubble With Special Rules (Sporadically Margaret)
・Lv.10 NARAKA(NAЯAKA)

* Internet connection required for purchase.
* Game must be restarted after songs are purchased in order to use them.
name: Touhou LostWord Song Pack
